library(readr)
library(tidyverse)
library(here)
library(janitor)
library(DataExplorer)

load("bike.RData")
load("ycomments.RData")
load("cervical.RData")
cervical <- clean_names(cervical)
bike <- clean_names(bike)
ycomments <- clean_names(ycomments)



plot_missing(bike)

plot_missing(ycomments)

plot_missing(cervical)

plot_bar(bike)

plot_bar(ycomments)
## 4 columns ignored with more than 50 categories.
## comment_id: 1953 categories
## author: 1792 categories
## date: 1710 categories
## content: 1736 categories

plot_bar(cervical)

plot_histogram(bike)

plot_histogram(cervical)

plot_correlation(na.omit(bike), maxcat = 5L)
## 2 features with more than 5 categories ignored!
## mnth: 12 categories
## weekday: 7 categories

plot_correlation(na.omit(cervical), maxcat = 5L)
